The paper deals with efficient learning algorithms for regression and eigenvector computation, which are core topics in machine learning and data analysis. The paper also mentions the use of acceleration techniques such as approximate proximal point and catalyst, which are commonly used in optimization and machine learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.NA (Numerical Analysis), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.CV (Computer Vision).
